Requirements:   

A Diploma or above holder in Environmental Science / Education / Communication / Social Science / Marketing or any relevant discipline, preferably with a University Degree and 3 years working experience;
English Language (Syllabus B) and Chinese Language at Grade E or above in HKCEE/Level 2 in HKDSE;
Sound knowledge of local environmental issues, especially in waste reduction, is preferred;
