As a key member in the corporate communications team, we are looking for a dynamic and motivated individual with positive attitude to promote effective communication between the company and the general media and ESG communities;
This will be an excellent opportunity for individuals with prior PR experience and passion in developing their knowledge in environmental, social and governance (ESG) issues to join an award winning industry leading player.

